OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mixed day of bright or sunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers throughout the day.
OL,7,FShowers may be heavy at times.
OL,8,FGradually becoming dry as showers
OL,9,Fclear to the east through the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry start to the evening with
OL,13,Flate sunny spells, but soon turning
OL,14,Fcloudy as rain spreads into eastern
OL,15,Fparts. Low cloud and heavy rain then
OL,16,Fspreading to all areas overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
