OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA wet start to the day with
OL,6,Frain and drizzle. Rain easing in the
OL,7,Fmorning to leave a breezy and cloudy
OL,8,Fday with just the odd outbreak of
OL,9,Flight rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,12,Fspells and breezy on Friday with a few
OL,13,Fshowers possible. Drier with sunny
OL,14,Fspells on Saturday. Dry on Sunday with
OL,15,Fhazy sunshine developing.
